<h2 id="susan-reed">Susan Reed</h2>
<p>It seemed endless. It seemed to start early in the morning, which it probably did. I canâ€™t remember what time it finished, but it seemed like for ever to a little one. But I can picture it in my mind, I can see her walking down and then I can see her coming away from the altar, carrying the sceptre. I think it was a sceptre in her hand. And all the little pageboys behind her trying to move the train and, oh it was a wonderful thing.</p>

