<h2 id="sylvia-cox">Sylvia Cox</h2>
<p>Youâ€™re brought up with stories of princesses and so forth, and golden carriages and whatever, but this really was it. Obviously we couldnâ€™t see the gold but we imagined it. And one of the things that really struck me and kept amazing me all the way through the day was the fact that I was here in Sunderland and we were seeing events, historic events that we would remember all our lives, hundreds of miles away in London. And it was as it happened, it wasnâ€™t just a film that we were seeing after it had been taken, it was something that was happening now, and it really was amazing.</p>

<h2 id="mary-taylor">Mary Taylor</h2>
